    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144908_48_5879-5935",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "5879-5935",
      "markText": "于是，国王希拉姆发现自己欠了宰相一笔巨债，他要么面对宰相源源不断的索求，要么砍掉他的头。我猜测他最终选择了后者。",
      "totalCount": 560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144908&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=5879&rangeEnd=5935",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ccd32570813ab9f1ag018737?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=5879&rangeEnd=5935"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144908_42_1709-1754",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "1709-1754",
      "markText": "因此，我希望每个读者都能在阅读的过程中尝试表达，无关文字多少，留个言，这本书便有了你的痕迹",
      "totalCount": 500,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144908&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=1709&rangeEnd=1754",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ccd32570813ab9f1ag018737?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=1709&rangeEnd=1754"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144908_49_7641-7681",
      "chapterUid": 49,
      "range": "7641-7681",
      "markText": "费马补充写道：“我已经发现了一个奇妙的证明方法，但这里的空白处太窄，我写不下。”",
      "totalCount": 486,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144908&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=7641&rangeEnd=7681",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ccd32570813ab9f1ag018737?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=7641&rangeEnd=7681"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144908_48_8637-8724",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "8637-8724",
      "markText": "事实上，这样一台自动印刷机将会印出自人类学会书写以来所写下的一切文字：所有的散文和诗歌，所有报纸上的社论和广告，所有厚重的科学论著，每一封情书，甚至每一张留给送奶工的便条……",
      "totalCount": 450,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144908&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=8637&rangeEnd=8724",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ccd32570813ab9f1ag018737?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=8637&rangeEnd=8724"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144908_5_748-846",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "748-846",
      "markText": "可是，在当时的环境下，伽莫夫感到自己的天性和想象力都受到了压抑。1932年，他和夫人试图坐木筏从黑海逃到土耳其，但是没有成功。1933年，趁着在比利时召开第七次索尔维会议的机会，伽莫夫离开了苏联。",
      "totalCount": 442,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144908&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=748&rangeEnd=846",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ccd32570813ab9f1ag018737?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=748&rangeEnd=846"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144908_7_1778-1808",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1778-1808",
      "markText": "最终接受了一个事实，即本书并不像我最初预想的那样适合儿童阅读",
      "totalCount": 384,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144908&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1778&rangeEnd=1808",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ccd32570813ab9f1ag018737?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1778&rangeEnd=1808"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144908_48_4518-4542",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "4518-4542",
      "markText": "事实上，在整个宇宙中，平均每立方米只有1个原子。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144908&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=4518&rangeEnd=4542",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ccd32570813ab9f1ag018737?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=4518&rangeEnd=4542"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144908_48_12307-12330",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "12307-12330",
